.html">今年二月</a>，该公司开始向加拿大、新西兰、葡萄牙和西班牙的用户收取额外费用，以便让不与他们住在一起的朋友和家人继续使用他们的帐户。该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-starts-charging-for-account-sharing-in-the-us-185133792.html">于五月将账户共享收费扩大到美国</a>。</p><p>第三方分析表明，在 Netflix 开始在美国执行该政策后不久，美国<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflixs-password-sharing-crackdown-seems-to-be-working-151023478.html">的帐户注册量激增</a>。当该公司下周公布季度收益结果时，我们很快就会更清楚地了解该战略对公司的效果如何。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/you-can-now-move-your-netflix-profile-to-an-existing-account-175539026.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/you-can-now-move-your-netflix-profile-to-an-existing-account-175539026.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 2af238f6-7e21-494b-ba76-da809b0e3a6b</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 17:55:39 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689098152</ingested><modified> 2023-07-11T17:55:56+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="3840" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/38417f80-f9ca-11ed-bf7f-c9d088c53703" width="5760"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3840" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/38417f80-f9ca-11ed-bf7f-c9d088c53703" width="5760"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc: