找到它在打折。</a></p><h2> AirPods Pro（第二代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="9db1163cc208437ab616bf0c92be17b1" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>苹果第二代<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZsFyWkcTnFzGQhOFRhEkhfJPKdgHXL1Hh0MECs4gO9X&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized%2Fdp%2FB0BDHWDR12%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">AirPods Pro</a>在 Prime Day 促销价为 199 美元。这些耳机比前代产品有了巨大的改进，提供了改进的音质、ANC 和透明模式。我们仍然认为它们是<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-wireless-earbuds-120058222.html">iPhone 用户的最佳耳塞，</a>因为它们具有 Apple 特有的功能，例如快速配对和切换以及免提 Siri。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>最新的 Pro 耳机看起来与之前的版本基本相同，但这是因为大部分变化都在内部。与其他 AirPods 一样， <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-pro-review-second-generation-130048218.html">AirPods Pro</a>也配备了 Apple 的 H1 芯片，该芯片支持大多数 iOS 和 macOS 特定的功能。如果您已经在 Apple 生态系统中根深蒂固，那么 AirPods Pro 将是您可以获得的最佳无线耳机。使用 Android 手机的用户应该考虑 Prime Day 促销的其他一些<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-amazon-prime-day-headphone-deals-163351574.html">耳机和耳塞</a>。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-pro-review-second-generation-130048218.html"><strong>阅读我们对 Apple AirPods Pro（第二代）的完整评论</strong></a></p><h2>AirPods（第 3 代） </h2><p><core-commerce id="94f15f8993104e9d91e84adb33766ce0" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Apple 更新版<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcejQJbPI1PdN662yBkoJqMQ16-P0v5Lze1FWLQeUrL8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%