新一代配备了大量新传感器，可以检测您的体温、提供心电图和血氧读数并提供改善的睡眠指标。即将推出的<a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-apple-watch-embraces-widgets-again-in-watchos-10-180838970.html">WatchOS 10</a>将利用其中的许多传感器，让您更深入地了解自己的日常健康状况。</p><h2>苹果 10.2 英寸 iPad </h2><p><core-commerce id="4938d84f00c646c5aac3c78702e3a86a" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>苹果第 9 代 iPad 在亚马逊的售价降至<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATa5mYiPu-M8vsoqPht6MpVoTlhIINBcVHeH4WJiNxjF&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F2021-Apple-10-2-inch-iPad-Wi-Fi%2Fdp%2FB09G9CJM1Z%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">250 美元</a>，创下历史新低。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASSuhUDXFc_cE0mx0-6SD48Uzl1_wNqh0LAdQ1eYTCjo&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2F2021-Apple-10-2-inch-iPad-Wi-Fi-64GB-Space-Gray-9th-Generation%2F483978365" class="rapid-with-clickid">沃尔玛</a>售价 279 美元。这是上一代标准 iPad，也是我们<a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">最佳 iPad 指南</a>中的预算选择。它是休闲浏览、畅玩流媒体和轻度游戏的绝佳沙发伴侣。</p><p>最新（第 10 代）64GB 尺寸的 iPad 在亚马逊上仅向 Prime 会员开放，售价为 380 美元，但<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Best Buy;elmt:;cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5e0bed65-d2f8-4b34-9b8f-955218c0e37a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Best+Buy&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI1ZTBiZWQ2NS1kMmY4LTRiMzQtOWI4Zi05NTUyMThjMGUzN2EiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYm