解成的碎片，以便模型可以更容易地处理它们——因此克劳德有能力“消化”用户数据。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这种能力的增强也将转化为更长、更细致的响应。<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.anthropic.com/index/claude-2">该公司宣布，</a> Claude 2 甚至能够生成“最多数千个代币”的短篇小说。其编码能力也有所提高，在<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://github.com/openai/human-eval">Codex HumanEval</a>基准测试中的得分从 56% 上升至 71.2%。</p><p>克劳德的“ <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/anthropic-explains-how-its-constitutional-ai-girds-claude-against-adversarial-inputs-160008153.html">宪法人工智能</a>”系统已经以<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/anthropics-claude-ai-is-guided-by-10-secret-foundational-pillars-of-fairness-193058471.html">公平和自治的 10 条“基本”原则</a>为指导。自第一个版本发布以来，红队进行了广泛的测试，使克劳德 2 成为一个情绪更加稳定、更难以愚弄 AI 的人。据报道，与其前身 Claude 2 相比，“与 Claude 1.3 相比，提供无害响应的能力提高了 2 倍”，该公司在声明中称。如果您已经订阅了 Claude 1.3 API，这是个好消息，您将自动转至 Claude 2，无需额外付费。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/anthropic-releases-claude-2-a-more-capable-less-gullible-ai-chatbot-160053168.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/anthropic-releases-claude-2-a-more-capable-less-gullible-ai-chatbot-160053168.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8ea284f2-3582-4cba-9640-0d975abfb56d</guid><dc:creator>安德鲁·塔兰托拉</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 16:00:53 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689095512</ingested><modified> 2023-07-11T17:11:55+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Andrew Tarantola]]></category><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/b7477c20-0597-11ee-bbff-7bf54c39e0e1" width="8000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_ht