data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAf6ev85_QKZnS483av-pt6wat20wilm4grwbONP0aBRA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLG-55-Inch-Refresh-AI-Powered-OLED55B2PUA%2Fdp%2FB09RMR23XL" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/LG-55-Inch-Refresh-AI-Powered-OLED55B2PUA/dp/B09RMR23XL?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">65 英寸型号的</a>售价为 1,197 美元。</p><p>我们还会注意到<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Best Buy;elmt:;cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=5e0bed65-d2f8-4b34-9b8f-955218c0e37a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Best+Buy&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdh4gZPfCo-nASCJPktalB8XrZsXtpQYGQjJyNgS7kvf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestbuy.com%2Fsite%2Flg-48-class-a2-series-oled-4k-uhd-smart-webos-tv%2F6501902.p" class="rapid-with-clickid">LG A2，48</a>英寸型号在百思买的售价降至 600 美元。如果你真的想要一个 OLED 显示屏，这个价格是一个不错的价格，尽管它的亮度进一步降低，刷新率仅限于 60Hz，并且缺乏用于游戏的 HDMI 2.1 功能。</p><h2>三星QN90B </h2><p><core-commerce id="eb48a08959444a38ad46c067ae35c079" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> 55 英寸型号的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:25;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAftn9YvZ7t3u457XuSWxABcu6Eip-fc65lJYTQox-rc9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09SBHSNNZ%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B09SBHSNNZ/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">三星 QN90B</a>价格回落至 1,098 美元。这不是我们见过的最好价格，但仍比通常的市场价格低 100 美元左右。如果您正在寻找较小的套装， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt