算紧张的人来说， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAV2wRDLC2GV-dE9l2uULkHD-4Y0a90oO6VPGgt-Rc4rI&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHisense-Mini-LED-Compatibility-1500-nit-55U8H%2Fdp%2FB0B5YZNZTZ" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/Hisense-Mini-LED-Compatibility-1500-nit-55U8H/dp/B0B5YZNZTZ?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">55 英寸的海信 U8H</a> 600 美元的价格非常超值。这仅比我们过去几个月大部分时间看到的价格低 50 美元左右，但它与电视的历史最低价持平。就性价比而言，U8H 的 Mini LED 背光、量子点和全阵列局部调光可提供令人印象深刻的对比度、亮度和黑色均匀性。它同时支持杜比视界和 HDR10+，其两个 HDMI 2.1 端口可以以流畅的 120Hz 播放 4K 内容。与上面的高端电视相比，它仍然有一个台阶，特别是在观看角度方面。但以这个价格来说，它很难超越，而且它应该可以在明亮或黑暗的房间里工作。</p><p>与此同时，刚刚发布的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:36;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAT-psWDWb8zPcNvDSee6wSNmJgxTIRMk1c68V-tDy_Bf&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHisense-Class-Mini-LED-Google-55U8K%2Fdp%2FB0C73H8PVT" class="rapid-with-clickid">海信 U8K</a>承诺提供 144Hz 刷新率和更多局部调光区域，但目前起价为 800 美元，我们还不能说它的实际升级幅度有多大。</p><h2> TCL 6系列R655 </h2><p><core-commerce id="359f681b469f4de7bf6cb8087a03a577" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:37;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQjdaWEdDVlk_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMThhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMzc4Y2MyMi0yMThkLTQ2YjAtYjA5MS04MDlkOWQ4NjQ3NmYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAYF7BSysH0ve1MZ0MetLGzIc575AraP4C3lFdQBsTfHL&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B7ZXGCVY" class="rapid-with-clickid">TCL 6 系列电视</a>55 英寸型号的价格降至 650 美元，比平常价格低了 30 美元左右。这是海信 U8H 的有力竞争对手：根据<a data-i13n="cpos:39;pos:1" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/reviews/best-lcd-led-tv/">网上的</a><a data-i13n="cpos:38;pos:1" href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/televisions/features/tcl-6-series-vs-hisense-u8h-which-should-you-buy">评论</a>，它的对比度和峰值亮度没有那么强，但就价格而言，它的表现仍然不错，如果您更喜欢 Roku OS 而不是海信 U8H，那么它可能值得一看。 U8H 的 Google TV 平台。</p><p> TCL 2023 年的几款电视也跌至新低，包括 400 美元的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:40;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASDKCQmAzWO5rlcLHTHUxdNXDe4AyeCnEcfqD10UqfPK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTCL-55Q650G-Accelerator-Streaming-Television%2Fdp%2FB0C1J5RZD8" class="rapid-with-clickid">55 英寸 Q6、550</a>美元的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:41;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcNSDdmFqreqZ9lyKDqe4evmEBtUbwmfRePDT94KSDQk&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTCL-55Q750G-Accelerator-Streaming-Television%2Fdp%2FB0C1J6FF6J" class="rapid-with-clickid">55 英寸 Q7</a>和 1,200 美元的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:42;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbzD2U-jNtSmGN2K0kIrjpWBt9pOv7bm2ldsJ0cuT7U1&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTCL-65QM850G-Accelerator-Streaming-Television%2Fdp%2FB0C1J4MPBB" class="rapid-with-clickid">65 英寸旗舰 QM8</a> 。不过，这些都不是 6 系列真正的一对一替代品。 Q7 是最接近的，但它缺少 6 系列电视的 Mini LED 背光。 QM8 确实采用 Mini LED 技术，但其定价可与 OLED 和更高端的 LCD 设备竞争。我们尚未测试新的 TCL 电视，其他地方的评论也很少，因此请将此视为 PSA，而不是完整的推荐。</p><h2>海信A6H </h2><p><core-commerce id="2d1f6b8c736d4551a4fb93406b0fcb11" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:43;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9IaXNlbnNlLTU1LUluY2gtVmlydHVhbC1DaHJvbWVjYXN0LTU1QTZIL2RwL0IwOVdRSlBXV1k_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMThhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMzc4Y2MyMi0yMThkLTQ2YjAtYjA5MS04MDlkOWQ4NjQ3NmYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAaaWO_bwhTpGujXbyqjCde7kmSzJclONdUqHb8DqIsF2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHisense-55-Inch-Virtual-Chromecast-55A6H%2Fdp%2FB09WQJPWWY" class="rapid-with-clickid">海信 A6H</a> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:44;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9IaXNlbnNlLTU1LUluY2gtVmlydHVhbC1DaHJvbWVjYXN0LTU1QTZIL2RwL0IwOVdRSlBXV1k_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMThhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMzc4Y2MyMi0yMThkLTQ2YjAtYjA5MS04MDlkOWQ4NjQ3NmYifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAaaWO_bwhTpGujXbyqjCde7kmSzJclONdUqHb8DqIsF2&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FHisense-55-Inch-Virtual-Chromecast-55A6H%2Fdp%2FB09WQJPWWY" class="rapid-with-clickid">50 英寸机型</a>售价降至 228 美元， <a data-i13n="el